# ║ Path(_get_symmetrized_forms(), return a list giving all possible permutations of self that are allowed by its symmetries) over Any ║
# ╠════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
# ║ _get_symmetrized_forms : Any → Any                         ║
# ╠════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
